# [NotesWordCount v2](http://dev.newtontalk.net/~dpadilla/progs.htm)
4 KB, Freeware by [[DanielPadilla]], 2004. Adds a "Count Words" option to the routing menu of the Notes Application. Version 2 adds letter and character counts and allows to select multiple notes in overview. Only counts in plain notes - no checklists or outlines.%%%
Great if you work on an article than needs to meet a certain size!%%%
